title: Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate 3/17/09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




March 17, 2009

 



Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate 3/17/09




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secrectary  ________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                            March 17, 2009 NOMINATIONS SENT TO THE SENATE: William V. Corr, of Virginia, to be Deputy Secretary of Health and Human Services, vice Tevi David Troy, resigned.    Kathleen Sebelius, of Kansas, to be Secretary of Health and Human Services.
